{
  "texts": [
    "Phishing emails, fraudulent ads, and software weaknesses disseminate it.",
    "Ransomware may cause considerable data loss, financial harm, and operational interruption until the ransom is paid or files are recovered from backups.",
    "Scareware tricks users into thinking their computer has a virus or other major problem to get them to buy needless or hazardous software.",
    "It usually appears as pop-up advertising or antivirus software-like security notifications.",
    "Scareware may cost money and install spyware or other malware if the user buys it or removes the phoney risks it claims to have found."
  ]
}